==市場營銷==
電影原片名為《The Huntsman》，直到2015年11月16日，從釋出的四款角色海報得知正式片名為《The Huntsman: Winter's War》<ref name="EWPoster">{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/16/charlize-theron-jessica-chastain-huntsman-winters-war-posters |title=See Charlize Theron, Jessica Chastain in new The Huntsman: Winter’s War character posters |first=Devon |last=Coggan |accessdate=November 16, 2015 |date=November 16, 2015 |publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |archive-date=2016-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813200236/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/16/charlize-theron-jessica-chastain-huntsman-winters-war-posters |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3天後，2015年11月18日，首支預告片在網上釋出<ref name="EWTrailer">{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/18/the-huntsman-winters-war-trailer |publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=November 18, 2015 |accessdate=November 18, 2015 |last=Coggan |first=Devon |title=Charlize Theron and Emily Blunt amass an army of darkness in The Huntsman: Winter’s War trailer |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126132514/https://ew.com/article/2015/11/18/the-huntsman-winters-war-trailer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==發行==
2014年7月31日，環球影業將《狩獵者：凜冬之戰》排於2016年4月22日在美國上映<ref name=ReleaseDeadline>{{cite news|title=Universal’s Snow White Prequel ‘Huntsman’ Targets April 2016 Release|url=http://deadline.com/2014/07/huntsman-movie-snow-white-sequel-release-date-april-22-2016-812885/|accessdate=August 1, 2014|publisher=Deadline.com|date=July 31, 2014|archivedate=2014年8月5日|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140805225453/http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/huntsman-movie-snow-white-sequel-release-date-april-22-2016/}}</ref>。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度16%，基於182條評論，平均分為4.2/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_huntsman_winters_war/ |title=The Huntsman: Winter's War (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=April 14, 2016 |archive-date=2016-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424153048/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_huntsman_winters_war |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到36分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-huntsman-winters-war |title=The Huntsman: Winter's War reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=April 5, 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118065138/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-huntsman-winters-war |dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6.1分。主要被影評人認為演員陣容強大，但敘事略為薄弱。大多讚賞其極度華麗精緻的場面及服裝，甚至有人認為該片應奪得奥斯卡最佳服裝及視覺藝術獎。

===票房===
《狩獵者：凜冬之戰》在美國上映前的兩週在十八個國家推出，首週末票房收入為1910萬美元（從3969個大銀幕）<ref name="Overseas17thOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/batman-v-superman-jungle-book-huntsman-winters-war-zootopia-london-has-fallen-china-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201734780/|title=‘Batman V Superman’ At $487.7M Offshore; ‘Jungle Book’ Swings With $31.7M; ‘Huntsman’ Misses Mark; ‘Zootopia’ Sets Dis China Record – Intl B.O. Final|author=Nancy Tartaglione|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=April 11, 2016|accessdate=April 12, 2016|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214101550/https://deadline.com/2016/04/batman-v-superman-jungle-book-huntsman-winters-war-zootopia-london-has-fallen-china-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201734780/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

北美首映週末的票房為2010萬美元，比預期的2400萬美元低。

在中国大陆，首周3天取得6900万人民币列第三位，最终票房1.06億人民币<ref>[http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/247184 《猎神：冬日之战》電影介紹] {{Wayback|url=http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/247184 |date=20201127115742 }} 貓眼票房</ref>。

